{"type": "article", "id": 41665, "title": "看个时间也可以烧脑，不过这次钟的外形相当古朴｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-06-05T23:00:38Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 36956, "name": "UM Project"}, {"id": 41166, "name": "La Fabrique DIY"}, {"id": 41167, "name": "Buster + Punch"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 143, "image": "img/article/article_show/201706052055285d8DsTxl3vfYANr9.png", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>The City Clock by La Fabrique DIY</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.lafabriquediy.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">La Fabrique DIY</a> 是一个法国的 DIY 网站，运营者 Lucas 和他的未婚妻 Claire 经常在上面分享自己的创意。一天傍晚，沿塞纳河散步的两人被河边亮着灯的窗户所吸引，决定设计一款以二进制显示时间的模型钟。The City Clock 的正面共有 16 扇窗户，从下往上分别代表了 1、2、4、8 四个数字，内部的小灯会随着时间变化点亮或是熄灭，就像是真的有人生活在其中一样。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1050329560/the-city-clock-paris-design\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，售价为 90 欧元。Lucas 还表示，他们未来或许会以其他城市的建筑为原型拓宽产品线。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605205606h1yEmXrM69e8obOl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605205607wveh97QJn5WSmqZF.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.547059\" data-format=\"png\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605205607HreGd7MXRskNyICi.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.498529\" data-format=\"png\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605205607CWyYphqKBeFEML0x.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.495588\" data-format=\"png\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605205607mHZwrSJALckblo6u.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.527941\" data-format=\"png\">\n</figure></div><h3>Caged by Buster + Punch</h3><p>以伦敦充满金属质感的都市天际线为灵感，英国家居品牌 <a href=\"https://www.busterandpunch.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Buster + Punch</a> 的创始人、建筑师 Massimo Minale 设计了一套名为 <a href=\"https://www.busterandpunch.com/lifestyle/caged\" rel=\"nofollow\">Caged</a> 的模块化灯饰。整个系列分为壁灯和吊灯两款，包括灯泡、品牌标志性的黑色开关、背板以及金属框在内的组件都可以根据需要进行替代，为房间加入工业风的元素。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605205623lcfunz2MHINx8ti3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.609951\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605205623ctCOx9nAHfkVguDM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605205624PHYZXjrCv5J1hLM7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.713895\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201706052056247Fk6YHPJqjiclMAD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.582068\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605205624IwJQRUctLFVSYb0k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714456\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><h3>Ultraframe collection by UM Project</h3><p>在今年的纽约设计周上，布鲁克林家具品牌 <a href=\"http://www.umproject.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">UM Project</a> 将建筑和交通工具设计中常见的元素引入传统的家具制作中，带来了由多种材料混搭而成的储物柜系列 Ultraframe，奇特的结构很容易让人联想到科幻作品中的设备和飞船舱。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605205639RnuIPQ4S5xmVUHDy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562606\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605205639ERHMdGeVk39DTFPA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605205640PsT5CxDV9vf1ydXI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000423\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201706052056392CHBlQSsq471mLv9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.497039\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><h3>PK.01 by Marion Lenne</h3><p>还记得将笔刀放在一旁，它突然沿着桌面滚动起来的惊悚时刻吗？为了提升这一常用工具的安全性，法国工业设计师 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/m-lenne\" rel=\"nofollow\">Marion Lenne</a> 构思了一款名为 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/52257677/PK01-Precision-Knife\" rel=\"nofollow\">PK.01</a> 的概念设计。由回收来的软木塞和橡胶制成的笔盖既可以保护刀头，又能沿着笔身旋转至刀头下方起到防滑的作用。Lenne 还采用相同的组合，为笔刀设计了配套的刻度尺，减轻了纯金属带来的冰冷感。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605205659Eg8stHcV1f9jMxZe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605205659A9FMa81u6H3JQdVb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605205658zirAE7eZtGwv93RJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201706052056599zdFshAx1RlnB7HO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605205658uJNt5Vm76kgITo1z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><h3>Howling Coast by Yuga Huang</h3><p>现居纽约的视觉设计师 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/YugaHuang\" rel=\"nofollow\">Yuga Huang</a> 为来自波特兰的精酿啤酒品牌 Howling Coast 设计了一个强调产地特色的<a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/49642865/Howling-Coast-Beer-Packaging\" rel=\"nofollow\">包装</a>。她以当地的国际神秘动物学博物馆（International Cryptozoology Museum）为灵感，绘制了看起来并不可怕的野人和海怪，并将它们和标志性的山林组合在一起。作为总结，她还特意设计了“由怪物和人类共同酿造”的标语印刷在罐身上。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605205717ZzD9cEuK7XqAJlmT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.380833\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605205718CWLnKbdpar6IUs48.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.359167\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605205718imNOTLIDz1XrFs6p.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.359167\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605205718brQWuZKRyYis5Xfo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.701667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><h3>Brushstroke Cakes by Kalabasa</h3><p>有些蛋糕，仅仅是看着就是一种享受。最近，位于莫斯科的 <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/kalabasa/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Kalabasa</a> 甜品店就推出了一系列让人舍不得下嘴的蛋糕。Kalabasa 的甜品师模仿笔刷制作了一批色彩斑斓的巧克力“羽毛”，再将它们和水果、花朵一起堆砌在蛋糕上，看起来就像是一幅幅可以吃的油画。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605205807T7QL5OKDrkMXH230.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.248571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605205806xFPbwrznBg62jfEQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.232857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605205806T3I6KaHFkiRSZcCh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170605205807RPL9q2wHTAUzxIF4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.250000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div>"}